title: Funchalense (The)
body: Only three issues of this newspaper were published, from July 2 to 21, 1847. Another periodical with the same title, of which Dr. Sebastião Frederico Rodrigues Leal was the editor, ran for 103 issues from April 17, 1859, to June 13, 1861. A third newspaper with the same title, of which only 9 issues were published, ran from September 1 to October 26, 1886.
